I'm reviewing the patch. IIUC according to [RFC-1831|https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1831] APPENDIX A: SYSTEM AUTHENTICATION, AUTH_SYS should also carry the following data structure:

{noformat}
      struct authsys_parms {
         unsigned int stamp;
         string machinename<255>;
         unsigned int uid;
         unsigned int gid;
         unsigned int gids<16>;
      };
{noformat}
